data.description: This charming and meticulously designed home, located in Wickenburg Ranch, Nestled in the peaceful neighborhood of Bonanza, this splendid residence boasts two bedrooms and two bathrooms, spread across just under 2000 square feet of living space. As you step into the backyard, you will be delighted to find low maintenance landscaping, adorned with a fire pit, a delightful pergola, and a covered patio, providing an idyllic space for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. This home is a true oasis, where modern living meets tranquility, ready to embrace its new owners with open arms. Residents also have access to a plethora of amenities, including a beautiful golf course, fitness center, a resort swimming pool, and much more.Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own.
